name: ThoracicAortaDisease
title: Thoracic aorta disease
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Represent codes indicating a patient has a disorder of the thoracic aorta),(Data Element Scope: CONDITION: CLINICAL_DRIVER:),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes acute diseases (e.g. dissection). 
Includes "other and unspecified" locations.
Includes congenital malformations.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes aortic disease that is specifically only for abdominal aorta.
Excludes injury to aorta.
Excludes simple atherosclerosis of the aorta.)
